text: Gábor Schaller (born 7 January 1966) is a Hungarian equestrian. He competed in the team eventing at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Hungary Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Budapest
